<p>You can see the corrections that you made during the stocktaking process by opening the item and clicking on <strong>Tab: Stock » Tab: Item movement</strong>.
In addition the import will be listed as an entry in the <strong>Stock » Incoming items</strong> menu. You can open the entry to see a list of the item that were changed (image 1).</p>
</div>
