<div class="paragraph">
<p>Activate the stocktaking mode for the warehouse that you want to carry out the stocktaking in. To do so, use the data format <strong>Stock</strong>. You need one export per warehouse.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Exporting stock:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <a href="/en/data/export-import/exporting-data">Data » Dynamic export</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>New data format</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the data format type <strong>Stock</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter a name for the data format.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Pay attention to the explanations given in table 2 and select the settings as desired. <br>
→ Further data fields and filters are optional.</p>
</li>
</ol>
